lead_paragraph: Jeff King, a four-time champion, was the first musher to reach the community of Ruby, Alaska, in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.

abstract: Four-time champion musher Jeff King is first to reach Ruby, Alaska, first checkpoint in Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
